Class JDBQuery2

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBQuery2
public class JDBQuery2
extends java.lang.Object
The JDBQuery is a utility class for building SQL queries generated by the user searching for data on one of the data admin screens. This class supersedes the original class JDBQuery2
